            <span class="utterance" who="#schwarzfitterJ" start="3202.602" end="x">I came to know [about her] through a comrade, who I happened to meet. So he told me he had met my sister. So I said, how do you know, my sister. So he said, I have inquired. Because everyone always inquired. One always questioned the other when people would meet: haven't you seen this one, haven't you seen that one? Each and everyone inquired about relatives. And I was with this comrade in the same <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a> for a year [?]; he knew me quite well, so he gave me a 'call of life.' He transmitted to me regards, and he told me that my sister ought to be either in Weiden, or in Spandau, that is in the Upper Palatinate [Pfalz]. So I took a trip there and I got together with her.</span>
